                     <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM GARDENER</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18541023-1088-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18541023-1088-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18541023-1088-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
